column1: This is as far as you can go, miss witch!
I am not a weird person!
Odd to see a longbow archer around here.
Are you here to hinder me, too?
Yes, I had an agreement with Sis earlier……
So no matter what, you are not allowed to move forward.
Well, I'm not interested in the things that lie ahead.
I'm just here to collect meteor fragments,
so could you let me pass? Pretty please?
If you want to, then you will have to ask my bow!
Well, let's see if you're a match for my magic…
That kind of kitty-level magic you've shown me is useless!
I shall bring you fear and regret.
